title: Euro-Tandoor
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Family-run Indian food cafe with some vegetarian food like dahl and a spicy veg wrap. The kitchen segregates meat from veg food. Dairy is used, so vegans should specify. Seats 24, has Wi-Fi. Located a block from the cruise ship docks near Prince George Wharf in downtown Nassau. Confirmed open by owner April 2015.
